INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (300,'002','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 is like gold being tempered in a furnace, ultimately forming a great vessel. Your capabilities, hardened through trials and efforts, will shine in the world, earning praise and respect from many people. The first half may have some challenging periods, but these are preparation processes for greater success, so maintain patience. As you move into the second half, the fruits of your labor will ripen and glorious moments will arrive. However, it is important not to be swayed by fleeting emotions but to maintain a positive mindset and steadily move forward.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
Financial fortune is generally stable, and you will receive rewards proportional to your efforts. In February and March, there is a possibility of unexpected income, so greet opportunities with a prepared attitude. April and August are times when you can gain wealth through others'' help, so it is good to pay attention to networking. Joint ventures or collaborative investments are more advantageous than individual investments, so move with trustworthy partners. However, excessive greed is forbidden, and caution is needed to avoid being easily swayed by unverified investment opportunities. If you manage finances thoroughly and refrain from excessive spending, you can establish a solid financial foundation by year''s end.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
This is a year when performance at work noticeably improves. June and July may bring opportunities for promotion or awards as your efforts and abilities are recognized. Approaching work with honesty and diligence will earn trust from superiors and colleagues. However, it is important not to be arrogant but to maintain a humble attitude. If you are considering starting a business, April or August are suitable times, and starting with sufficient preparation and planning can yield good results. In November, there will be joyful events in your household that will positively impact your work life.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
Love fortune rises after mid-year. Singles have a high chance of meeting good matches in March and August, so actively meet people. You can especially meet benefactors in the northeast or northwest directions. For married couples, relationships with spouses become stronger in February, and harmonious energy fills the home. However, in April and September, misunderstandings may arise in romantic relationships, so refrain from reckless behavior and act prudently. Be careful to avoid unnecessary gossip, and in November, it is good to pay attention to the health of your spouse or close family members.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Health fortune is generally good, but attention must be paid to excessive drinking and overwork. In January and February, you can find mental and physical stability, but if you do not moderate alcohol consumption, it can harm your health. In May, maintain health with regular lifestyle habits and balanced meals. In summer, sufficient hydration and rest are necessary, and in November, carefully observe the health conditions of your spouse or parents and recommend regular checkups. Stress management is important, so maintain mental and physical balance through leisurely activities like meditation, yoga, and walks.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
Relationships are generally harmonious, but a cautious attitude is necessary. In August and September, benefactors will appear to help, so actively expand your network. Since partnerships and cooperative relationships are keys to success, meeting good partners is important. However, if you trust people wrongly, you can suffer losses, so thoroughly verify others before forming relationships. Even with close people, it is good to draw clear lines in financial matters, and at year''s end, disputes and gossip may arise, so be careful with words and maintain a humble attitude.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
This is a very favorable year for knowledge expansion and skill acquisition. In October, new learning opportunities will come, and moving in the northeast or north-south directions can help you meet good teachers or mentors. If you are planning to obtain certifications or pursue degree programs, do not hesitate to challenge yourself. In December, your past efforts will bear fruit and opportunities to leap to new stages will come. Since consistent self-development guarantees future success, do not be lazy but diligently persevere.','January may bring matters that need to be handled discreetly as the new year begins. Be careful of legal issues and ensure there are no mistakes in documents. Like flowers blooming on one branch while leaves fall on another, joy and sorrow may alternate, but if you respond carefully, blessings will follow.

Financial fortune is stable, but it is better to avoid large investments. At work, build trust through diligent work attitudes. Health-wise, be careful of winter colds and respiratory diseases, and keep your body warm.

Relationships should be approached cautiously. Exchange New Year''s greetings but refrain from excessive promises, and form relationships within practical limits. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being white and blue.','February is a month when benefactors come to help, like plum blossoms blooming by a bright moonlit window. Even in difficult situations, unexpected helpers will appear, so do not lose hope. If you are considering moving or changing jobs, this month is a good time, and you can gradually move in better directions through changes.

Financial fortune rises and unexpected income is possible. Good news may arrive around the 15th, so greet opportunities with a positive mind. At work, tasks proceed smoothly and you can gain recognition from superiors.

At home, relationships with spouses strengthen and families can spend harmonious time together. Health is good but be careful of overeating and maintain fitness through moderate exercise. The southern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being red and gold.','March is a month with romantic connections, like flower buds flying in spring breezes. As auspicious stars shine on your door, blessings naturally come bringing joy. Singles have a high chance of meeting good matches, so actively participate in gatherings or blind dates. You may expand your family or have joyful events, so have a prepared mindset.

This is when financial fortune reaches its peak. If you have been considering investment or business expansion, this month is optimal. Especially after the 15th is more auspicious. Office workers may be assigned important projects or promotion opportunities may arrive.

Health-wise, be careful of spring seasonal colds and mind indoor-outdoor temperature differences. If you have allergies, it is good to prepare in advance. East and southeast directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being light green and sky blue.','April is a month when joyful events occur, like a dragon obtaining a wish-fulfilling jewel. Business ventures will surely prosper and proceed without problems. Cooperating with others to promote work can bring great wealth, so trust in the power of collaboration. However, special caution is needed regarding romantic relationships, and reckless behavior can invite gossip, so act prudently.

Financial fortune is favorable. Others'' wealth coincidentally comes to you bringing profit, making joint ventures or cooperative investments advantageous. At work, teamwork is important during this period, so focus on cooperating with colleagues.

Health is good but avoid overwork and get sufficient rest. Spring outdoor activities help physical and mental health. The western direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being yellow and orange.','May is a month of growth like plants meeting spring rain. With people''s help and cooperation, won''t all hundred matters proceed smoothly? As flower buds sit on willow branches singing, everything turns to gold. Blessings come to those who walk the righteous path, so acting correctly and honestly brings no worries to your body and benefits to your wealth.

Financial fortune is stable and continuous. Income earned through legitimate methods steadily increases, so work diligently. Dishonest methods or shortcuts are absolutely forbidden. At work, maintaining principled attitudes earns trust and recognition.

Paying attention to health management allows for a very healthy month. Regular lifestyle habits and balanced meals are important. In relationships too, honest and frank attitudes create good reputations. The northern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being black and navy.','June is a month like being an immortal, leisurely singing in a pavilion with a wine bottle nearby. Even if not good things, joyful events will occur, but on the other hand, health requires attention. Especially refrain from excessive drinking and thoroughly manage your body. This is a time to make a name through legitimate work, so you can earn a reputation for virtue in the world.

Career fortune rises. Promotion or award opportunities may come, so actively demonstrate your abilities. If you have important presentations or announcements, approach them confidently. Starting a business or expanding operations will bring good results.

Financial fortune also rises, so if investment opportunities come, proceed after careful review. At home, joyful news arrives and all family members can spend happy times. Health-wise, be cautious of summer heat. The southeast direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being green and gold.','July is a month when seeking a leopard on a mountain will surely succeed. Work will definitely be accomplished. Since profits lie in the northeast and north-south, starting work in those directions will bring help from the north among invisible benefactors. Maintain close relationships and move actively.

Financial and business fortune are very robust. New business opportunities or investment proposals may come, so review positively. Business trips or travels to northeast or northwest regions bring great profits. Work performance is also outstanding during this period of recognition.

However, abandoning arrogance and maintaining humility yields even better results. Do not be complacent with small successes but always approach with a learning attitude. Health-wise, be cautious of extreme heat and maintain sufficient hydration. The northeast direction is most auspicious, with lucky colors being white and silver.','August is a month when two hearts unite as one. However, getting close to the opposite sex will make it hard to avoid future troubles, so be careful. You will finally form a great vessel, establishing your name widely and enjoying wealth and honor. Benefactors try to help you, so cooperating with others will surely accomplish tasks.

Connections and cooperation are keys to success. You may meet important people or receive good proposals, so focus on networking. Joint ventures or partnerships will bring great achievements. At work, team projects are successfully completed and recognized.

Financial fortune is also very good. People of small blessings help you, potentially bringing unexpected income. Health is good but avoid overwork. The northwest direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being gold and purple.','September is a month when staying home brings no profit but going out brings wealth. It is worth considering something different from your usual work for a while. When the moon appears in bright skies illuminating heaven and earth, how can it be dark? Since wealth lies in the east, starting work in that direction will lead to success.

Financial fortune is comprehensively good. Opportunities come from everywhere, so be active. Business trips or business expansion toward the north and south are particularly advantageous. At work, you are recognized for achievements in various projects.

However, be especially careful of gossip or misunderstandings due to romantic issues. Establishing clear boundaries and acting prudently can avoid problems. Health-wise, be cautious of seasonal colds and focus on strengthening immunity. The eastern direction is most auspicious, with lucky colors being red and orange.','October is a month with definite good fortune in the east. When you start work, the end will connect to profit. However, if you use people wrongly, they will cause harm, so be careful with personnel management. It is important to be prudent in hiring and recruit verified talent.

This is a favorable month for business expansion or new market development. Business trips, travels, and overseas work lead to great achievements. Work related to northeast or north-south regions is even better. Office workers find field work or assigned duties helpful for career development.

This is also a good period for academics or self-development. Seeking new learning opportunities will help you meet excellent teachers or mentors. Health-wise, strengthen fitness through outdoor activities. Autumn mountain climbing or travel energizes body and mind. The eastern direction is most auspicious, with lucky colors being brown and beige.','November is a month when the bright full moon fills rooms with the warmth of autumn. You will surely meet someone you miss or have joyful events in your household. If not prohibited by the past, your family will be harmonious and joyful events will occur bringing warmth. However, making wrong friends easily causes harm, so being careful allows you to avoid misfortune.

Good news comes from work or business. Promotions, awards, contract closures and other joyful events occur, but beware of surrounding jealousy and envy they may cause. Share success with humble attitudes and express gratitude.

Family health requires attention. Especially carefully observe health conditions of spouses or parents and recommend regular checkups. Do not neglect small symptoms and address them early. Financial fortune is stable but prepare for possible medical expenses. The western direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being white and gray.','December is a month when wealth follows you. You will achieve wishes and gain wealth, so that wealth advances, expanding your foundation and filling it with profit. However, making wrong friends is easily harmful, so maintain prudence in relationships and form deep relationships only with verified people.

This is a period for wrapping up the year while establishing a foundation for new leaps forward. Financial fortune peaks, allowing you to achieve targeted financial plans. Year-end bonuses or unexpected income are highly likely.

Wrap up the year with gratitude and set new plans for next year. Health-wise, be cautious of year-end overwork and gatherings and get sufficient rest. All directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being gold and silver. Conclude the year with humility and gratitude.','2025-03-02 03:02:00.867978+00','e');
